{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"506bc4cc0b","title":"对薄一波来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"552abf3e41","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"506bc4cc0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"eb20f03aa7","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、国务院副总理。“文化大革命”中受到追害。1978年12月，中共十一届三中全会审查和纠正了过去对他的错误结论，肯定了他对党和人民的贡献，使他得到了平反昭雪。"},{"id":"1b4c600e27","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在薄一波1966年8月21日给毛泽东的信上。信中说：8月18日天安门上主席跟我握手并亲切他励要我好好革命时，我深受感动。“最近主席如果有时间，希望找我谈一次。我想主要谈两个问题：（一）工交各部当前文化大革命的主要情况；同时检查我在运动中所犯的错误；及我的一个请求。（二）我对改革工业体制的一个设想。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"83b94e44de","type":"title","text":"对薄一波“来信的批语？","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b"},{"id":"eb20f03aa7","type":"paragraph","text":"印发常委、文革小组及薄一波同志。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b"},{"id":"1b4c600e27","type":"paragraph","text":"请一波同志将一个请求和一个设想，先用书面告我，然后谈话，可以缩短谈的时间。你是一个爱讲长话的人，我有点害怕听三四小时那样的长话","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b"},{"id":"fdd857bb65","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b"},{"id":"ddf6f3a5de","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十一日夜","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b"}],"page":{"id":"7b66c41a88","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"506bc4cc0b","start":520,"end":520}}}},"__N_SSG":true}